                |Personalised
              .description
                |All of our services are on demand, and it’s only up to you whether to choose full-package or just a few of them.

            .item.columns.large-6.medium-6
              .image-wrap-outer
                .image-wrap ng-include="'/assets/rf-functional-test.svg'"
