            .item.columns.large-6.medium-6
              .image-wrap-outer
                .image-wrap ng-include="'/assets/rf-functional-test.svg'"
              .header
                |Risk-free
              .description
                |Guaranteed money back if you are dissatisfied with our service. No questions asked.

            .item.columns.large-6.medium-6
              .image-wrap-outer
                .image-wrap ng-include="'/assets/rf-functional-test.svg'"
              .header
                |Flexible packages
              .description
                |We’re best in what we do, that’s why you’ll get your results in 48 hours. If you are a lucky owner or manager of a complex product, we’ll take a little more time to make you happy. Our testers will provide you with clear and comprehensive reports in the convenient form, using the same bug-tracking system you do.

